# Clonnect - Development Standards

## 1. Project Overview

Clonnect is an AI-powered DM automation platform for content creators. It connects to Instagram, WhatsApp, and Telegram, auto-responds to followers using a fine-tuned LLM (Scout FT v2), manages leads through a CRM pipeline, handles bookings/payments, and provides audience intelligence вЂ” all via a React dashboard.

## 2. Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| **Backend** | Python 3.11, FastAPI, SQLAlchemy 2.0, Alembic |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL + pgvector (Neon) |
| **LLM (DM)** | Scout FT v2 via DeepInfra LoRA (primary), Groq fallback (BASE) |
| **LLM (fallback)** | GPT-4o-mini via OpenAI |
| **LLM (generation)** | Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite |
| **Frontend** | React 18.3, Vite 5.4, TypeScript 5.8, Tailwind 3.4, shadcn/ui |
| **State** | TanStack React Query 5, React Context |
| **Deploy** | Railway (single service: backend serves frontend SPA) |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions (test, lint, auto-merge claude branches) |

